<h2>What is Particle Physics?</h2>

<p>
Particle physics is the study of the most elementary constituents of 
matter---the building blocks of our universe. Physicists have created a theory that
describes these interactions to a very high level of accuracy. This theory invovles
12 particles of matter, and 3 of the 4 forces in Nature. This theory is the 
<a href="http://youtu.be/V0KjXsGRvoA">standard model</a>
of particle physics.
</p>

<p>
More to come on this...
</p>

